"{\"uid\": \"nbcbayarea.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-paris-garbage-collectors-lift-strike-threat-olympics-3538678\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hosting an international event like the Olympics has not exactly been a climate-friendly thing to do, but Paris 2024 wants to change that.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.488582109252955e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The home of the UN's landmark Paris Climate Agreement has reworked nearly every aspect of hosting the Olympics in order to become the first carbon-neutral games.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9999794943541158, \"rank\": 1.5971130083659732e-05, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Climate Agreement\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National climate reporter Chase Cain takes us behind the scenes in Paris to see how they plan to achieve that ambitious goal.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Bank\", \"score\": 0.9018939604540946, \"rank\": 0.10524842228326357, \"text\": \"Chase\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Bank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chase_Bank\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cain_and_Abel\", \"score\": 0.9709101194145762, \"rank\": 0.02973367305708981, \"text\": \"Cain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cain_and_Abel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cain_and_Abel\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998850892163, \"rank\": 1.1491071714435753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Editor's note: A previous version of this story made an comparison between the average carbon emissions from recent Olympic Summer Games and the emissions of India and Germany.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.979896962788521, \"rank\": 0.017248094696618907, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.5813570708074361, \"rank\": 0.7180835096612393, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This comparison was incorrect and has been removed from the story.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris garbage collectors have lifted the strike notice that threatened to leave the French capital facing piles of rubbish during theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998850892163, \"rank\": 1.1491071714435753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9637397622827694, \"rank\": 0.029031479387451823, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris City Hall said Wednesday it had sealed a deal with the workers and that the strike notice covering several days in May and a period from July to Sept. 8 had been lifted.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  TheParis Olympic Gameswill take place July 26-Aug. 11, followed by the2024 Paralympicsthat begin Aug. 28 and conclude Sept. 8.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}, {\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Bay Area\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNTV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An increase in the allowance system has been approved: 50 euros ($54) gross per month from July 2024, then 30 euros ($32.5) gross per month from January 2025,\\\" Paris City Hall said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the framework for bonuses for the workers who will be mobilized during the Olympic and Paralympic Games \\\"remains between 600 euros ($650) and 1,900 euros ($2,060), depending on the degree of intensification of the workload during the preparation, organization and/or participation in the staging\\\" of the event.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year,thousands of tons of rubbishremained on the Paris streets during a long strike by garbage collectors protesting a reform of the French pension system.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998850892163, \"rank\": 1.1491071714435753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1839, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9637397622827694, \"rank\": 0.029031479387451823, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}]}"